1973年[[鲁道夫·耶尼施|鲁道夫·耶尼施]]通过引入外源DNA进入胚胎，使得它创造了一个转基因小鼠——世界上第一个转基因动物。<ref>Jaenisch, R. and Mintz, B. (1974 ) Simian virus 40 DNA sequences in DNA of healthy adult mice derived from preimplantation blastocysts injected with viral DNA. Proc. Natl. Acad. 71(4):1250–1254 [http://www.pnas.org/content/71/4/1250] {{Wayback|url=http://www.pnas.org/content/71/4/1250 |date=20190707123834 }}</ref>詹尼士正在研究感染猿猴空泡病毒40 （[[SV40|SV40]]）的哺乳动物细胞时，他偶然读到[[Beatrice_Mintz|Beatrice Mintz]]描述的[[嵌合体|嵌合体]]小鼠的产生。他把他的SV40样品带到Mintz的实验室，并注射到小鼠的早期胚胎中，期待肿瘤发展。小鼠外表正常，但使用放射性探针后，他发现该病毒基因已整合到小鼠的基因组中<ref>{{cite journal|pages=13982–13984|title=Biography of Rudolf Jaenisch|volume=101|issue=39|date=2004-09-28|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences|url=http://www.pnas.org/cgi/doi/10.1073/pnas.0406416101|accessdate=2018-04-02|author=Christen Brownlee|doi=10.1073/pnas.0406416101}}</ref>然而，小鼠被转入的基因并没有传递给自己的后代。 1981年Frank Ruddle, Frank Constantini 和Elizabeth Lacy的实验室将纯化的DNA导入单细胞小鼠胚胎，使转入的基因传递到小鼠的后代。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Integration and stable germ line transmission of genes injected into mouse pronuclei|journal=Science|date=1981-12-11|doi=10.1126/science.6272397|url=http://science.sciencemag.org/content/214/4526/1244|language=en|volume=214|issue=4526|pages=1244–1246|issn=0036-8075|accessdate=2018-04-02|author=J. W. Gordon, F. H. Ruddle|archive-date=2020-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200711073406/https://science.sciencemag.org/content/214/4526/1244|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.nature.com/doifinder/10.1038/294092a0|pages=92–94|title=Introduction of a rabbit β-globin gene into the mouse germ line|journal=Nature|volume=294|issue=5836|issn=1476-4687|date=1981/11|language=En|accessdate=2018-04-02|doi=10.1038/294092a0|author=Franklin Costantini, Elizabeth Lacy}}</ref>

被首个报道进行遗传修饰的植物是1983年的烟草<ref>{{cite journal|title=Genetically Engineered Plants and Foods: A Scientist's Analysis of the Issues (Part I)|date=2008-04-29|doi=10.1146/annurev.arplant.58.032806.103840|journal=Annual Review of Plant Biology|pages=771–812|volume=59|issue=1|issn=1543-5008|url=http://www.annualreviews.org/doi/10.1146/annurev.arplant.58.032806.103840|accessdate=2018-04-02|author=Peggy G. Lemaux|archive-date=2019-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190331015538/https://www.annualreviews.org/doi/10.1146/annurev.arplant.58.032806.103840|dead-url=no}}</ref>它是由克尔·贝文、理查德·弗拉维尔和玛丽 - 戴尔奇尔顿首创的：通过创建一个[[嵌合基因|嵌合基因]]，结合抗生素抗性基因和农杆菌的Ti质粒。烟草被用该质粒转化的农杆菌感染，嵌合基因随之被插入到植物的基因组。通过组织培养技术，被抗生素选择、含有该基因的单一烟草细胞生长为新植株。<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.nature.com/doifinder/10.1038/304184a0|pages=184–187|title=A chimaeric antibiotic resistance gene as a selectable marker for plant cell transformation|journal=Nature|volume=304|issue=5922|issn=1476-4687|date=1983/07|language=En|accessdate=2018-04-02|doi=10.1038/304184a0|author=Michael W. Bevan, Richard B. Flavell, Mary-Dell Chilton}}</ref>

===对转基因技术发明者的承认===
2013年6月19日转基因技术发明团队的带头人被授予[[世界粮食奖|世界粮食奖]]，三个相互竞争的队伍在1983年1月首次提出他们的结果：孟山都的[[罗伯特·傅瑞磊|罗伯特·傅瑞磊]]、比利时根特大学学者、[[植物基因系统公司|植物基因系统公司]]和[[CropDesign|CropDesign]]公司的创始人马克·范·蒙塔古，以及隶属于华盛顿大学和[[先正达公司|先正达公司]]的玛丽 - 戴尔奇尔顿圣路易斯。25万美元的奖金，是颁发给改善世界食品的“质量，数量或可获取性”的人。<ref name=NYT61913>{{cite news|title=Executive at Monsanto Wins Global Food Honor|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/06/20/business/monsanto-executive-is-among-world-food-prize-winners.html|accessdate=June 20, 2013|newspaper=The New York Times|date=June 19, 2013|author=Andrew Pollack|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112023416/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/06/20/business/monsanto-executive-is-among-world-food-prize-winners.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==监管==
基因工程技术的发展在科学界引起了对潜在风险的担忧。关于基因工程的监管框架的建立始于1975年，在加利福尼亚州的[[阿西罗马|阿西罗马]]。[[阿西罗马关于重组DNA的会议|阿西罗马会议]]提出了一套关于谨慎使用重组技术和从该技术所产生的产品的指导方针。<ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.1073/pnas.72.6.1981|journal=Proc. Nat. Acad. Sci. USA|volume=72|issue=6|pages=1981–1984|year=1975|title=Summary Statement of the Asilomar Conference on Recombinant DNA Molecules|author=Berg, P., Baltimore, D., Brenner, S., Roblin, R. O., and Singer, M. F.|pmid=806076|pmc=432675|bibcode = 1975PNAS...72.1981B }}</ref>阿西洛马会议提出的建议是自愿遵守的，但在1976年[[国立卫生研究院_(美国)|美国卫生研究所]]（NIH）成立了一个重组DNA咨询委员会<ref>{{cite journal|journal=South Calif Law Rev|year=1978|volume=51|issue=6|pages=1435–50|title=Research on recombinant DNA molecules: the regulatory issues|author=Hutt, P.B.|url=http://heinonline.org/HOL/LandingPage?collection=journals&handle=hein.journals/juraba21&div=32&id=&page=|pmid=11661661|access-date=2021-01-20|archive-date=2019-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191108111944/https://heinonline.org/HOL/LandingPage?collection=journals&handle=hein.journals%2Fjuraba21&div=32&id=&page=|dead-url=no}}</ref>随后其他监管办公室建立（[[美国农业部|美国农业部]]（USDA），[[美国环境保护署|美国环境保护署]]（EPA）和[[美国食品及药物管理局|美国食品及药物管理局]]（FDA）），有效地使在美国所有的重组DNA研究受到严格的监管。<ref name="McHughen2007">{{cite journal|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1111/j.1467-7652.2007.00300.x|pages=071024233955001–???|title=US regulatory system for genetically modified [genetically modified organism (GMO), rDNA or transgenic] crop cultivars|journal=Plant Biotechnology Journal|volume=0|issue=0|date=2008-01-01|issn=1467-7652|language=en|accessdate=2018-04-02|doi=10.1111/j.1467-7652.2007.00300.x|author=Alan McHughen, Stuart Smyth}}</ref>1982年，[[经济合作与发展组织|经济合作与发展组织]]（OECD）发布的一份报告称存在释放转基因生物进入环境的潜在危害，因为当时正在开发第一个转基因植物。<ref>{{cite book|author=Bull, A.T., Holt, G. and Lilly, M.D.|year=1982|title=Biotechnology : international trends and perspectives|publisher=Organisation for Economic Co-operation and Development|location=Paris|url=http://www.oecd.org/dataoecd/34/9/2097562.pdf|access-date=2014-01-27|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924113014/http://www.oecd.org/dataoecd/34/9/2097562.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>随着技术的改进和接受基因改造的生物从[[模式生物|模式生物]]转移到潜在的商业产品，美国在科学技术办公室（OSTP）下成立了一个委员会，建立机制规范发展中的转基因技术。<ref name="McHughen2007"/>1986年OSTP给USDA、FDA和EPA分配了美国境内基因改造植物的批准权。<!--此句翻译不确定，求改正--><ref>{{cite journal|journal=Fed Regist.|year=1986|volume=51|issue=123|pages=23302–50|title=Coordinated framework for regulation of biotechnology|author=U.S. Office of Science and Technology Policy|url=http://usbiotechreg.nbii.gov/CoordinatedFrameworkForRegulationOfBiotechnology1986.pdf|pmid=11655807|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110516173328/http://usbiotechreg.nbii.gov/CoordinatedFrameworkForRegulationOfBiotechnology1986.pdf|archivedate=2011-05-16|access-date=2014-01-27}}</ref>在20世纪80年代末90年代初，包括[[粮农组织|粮农组织]]和[[世卫组织|世卫组织]]在内，许多组织提出了评估基因改造食物安全性的方针。<ref>WHO (1987): Principles for the Safety Assessment of Food Additives and Contaminants in Food, Environmental Health Criteria 70. World Health Organization, Geneva</ref><ref>WHO (1991): Strategies for assessing the safety of foods produced by biotechnology, Report of a Joint FAO/WHO Consultation. World Health Organization, Geneva</ref><ref>WHO (1993): Health aspects of marker genes in genetically modified plants, Report of a WHO Workshop. World Health Organization, Geneva</ref><ref>WHO (1995): Application of the principle of substantial equivalence to the safety evaluation of foods or food components from plants derived by modern biotechnology, Report of a WHO Workshop. World Health Organization, Geneva</ref>

==进一步工作==
携带经拷贝的[[癌基因|癌基因]]的遗传修饰小鼠于1984年被培育出，用来诱发它们的癌症。<ref name =Hanahan>{{cite journal|title=The origins of oncomice: a history of the first transgenic mice genetically engineered to develop cancer|date=2007-09-15|doi=10.1101/gad.1583307|language=en|journal=Genes & Development|volume=21|issue=18|url=http://genesdev.cshlp.org/content/21/18/2258|pages=2258–2270|issn=0890-9369|accessdate=2018-04-02|author=Douglas Hanahan, Erwin F. Wagner, Richard D. Palmiter|archive-date=2019-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191209235415/http://genesdev.cshlp.org/content/21/18/2258|dead-url=no}}</ref>遗传修饰技术也被用来进行小鼠[[基因敲除|基因敲除]]。第一次有记载的[[基因敲除小鼠|基因敲除小鼠]]是由[[马里奥·卡佩奇|马里奥·卡佩奇]]，[[马丁·埃文斯|马丁·埃文斯]]和[[奥利弗•史密斯|奥利弗•史密斯]]于1989年培育的。它们被用来研究各个基因的功能，是研究人类疾病的有用模型。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.genome.gov/12514551|title=Knockout Mice|publisher=National Human Genome Research Institute|accessdate=2014-01-27|archive-date=2018-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181216073853/https://www.genome.gov/12514551/|dead-url=no}}</ref>1992年制造出敲除[[肿瘤抑制基因|肿瘤抑制基因]]产生的癌症小鼠。<ref name =Hanahan/>制造[[基因敲除大鼠|基因敲除大鼠]]更加困难，直到2003年才实现<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nature.com/news/1998/030512/full/news030512-17.html |title=naturenews, 19 May 2003 |accessdate=2014-01-27 |archive-date=2019-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190408172155/http://www.nature.com/news/1998/030512/full/news030512-17.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://molpharm.wisc.edu/Faculty/fac_pages/gould/Pub12754522.pdf |title=Y Zan et al., Production of knockout rats using ENU mutagenesis and a yeast-based screening assay, Nat. Biotechnol. (2003). |accessdate=2014-01-27 |archive-date=2010-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100611201320/http://molpharm.wisc.edu/Faculty/fac_pages/gould/Pub12754522.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

因为并非所有的植物细胞都易受根癌农杆菌感染，所以其它方法被开发，包括[[电穿孔|电穿孔]]，[[微注射|微注射]]<ref>{{cite web | last = Peters | first = Pamela | title = Transforming Plants - Basic Genetic Engineering Techniques | url = http://www.accessexcellence.org/RC/AB/BA/Transforming_Plants.php | accessdate = 28 January 2010 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100316174245/http://www.accessexcellence.org/RC/AB/BA/Transforming_Plants.php | archivedate = 2010年3月16日 }}</ref>和用[[基因枪|基因枪]]进行粒子轰击（发明于1987）<ref>{{cite web | last = Voiland | first = Michael | coauthors = McCandless, Linda | title = Development Of The "Gene Gun" At Cornell | url = http://www.nysaes.cornell.edu/pubs/press/1999/genegun.html | accessdate = January 19, 2013 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080501203428/http://www.nysaes.cornell.edu/pubs/press/1999/genegun.html | archivedate = 2008年5月1日 }}</ref><ref>Roger Segelken for the Cornell Chronicle. Mary 14, 1987. Biologists Invent Gun for Shooting Cells with DNA Issue available as pdf download [http://ecommons.cornell.edu/bitstream/1813/25239/1/018_33.pdf here] {{Wayback|url=http://ecommons.cornell.edu/bitstream/1813/25239/1/018_33.pdf |date=20131029191933 }}, page 3</ref>

为了使基因被纳入每个细胞，必须进行[[植物组织培养|植物组织培养]]。组织培养系统，必须针对每一个植物物种开发，其中一些比另一些更容易。方法已经被发展，例如使用真空渗入（1993），或仅仅浸渍农杆菌溶液（2008）的[[拟南芥|拟南芥]]''(Arabidopsis thaliana)''花可制备转基因种子。<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1046/j.1365-313x.1998.00343.x|pages=735–743|title=Floral dip: a simplified method forAgrobacterium-mediated transformation ofArabidopsis thaliana|journal=The Plant Journal|volume=16|issue=6|date=1998-12-01|issn=1365-313X|language=en|accessdate=2018-04-02|doi=10.1046/j.1365-313x.1998.00343.x|author=Steven J. Clough, Andrew F. Bent}}</ref>在20世纪80年代新技术被开发出来，用来将分离叶绿体导入去壁植物细胞。与1987年推出的[[基因枪|基因枪]]结合就可以通过将外源基因整合到[[叶绿体|叶绿体]]来实现转基因。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.lifesciencesfoundation.org/events-item-799.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-03-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130330150255/http://www.lifesciencesfoundation.org/events-item-799.html |archivedate=2013-03-30 }}</ref>

基因工程已经被用于生产蛋白质，那些通常不能化学合成，而是来自于人类和其它生物来源的蛋白质。利用细菌合成人胰岛素在1979年被首创，第一次在1982年被用来治疗。<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1021/bp00018a001|pages=469–478|title=Recombinant human insulin|journal=Biotechnology Progress|volume=8|issue=6|date=1992-11-01|issn=1520-6033|language=en|accessdate=2018-04-02|doi=10.1021/bp00018a001|author=Michael R. Ladisch, Karen L. Kohlmann}}</ref>1988年第一次利用植物生产人类抗体。<ref name ="antibodies"/>1997年出于提取，净化和销售它的目的，[[抗生物素蛋白|抗生物素蛋白]]，一种鸡蛋蛋白，首次在植物中被表达。<ref name ="antibodies">{{cite journal|title=Plant molecular farming: systems and products|journal=Plant Cell Reports|doi=10.1007/s00299-004-0767-1|url=https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s00299-004-0767-1|date=2004-05-01|volume=22|issue=10|language=en|pages=711–720|issn=0721-7714|accessdate=2018-04-02|author=M. E. Horn, S. L. Woodard, J. A. Howard|archive-date=2019-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190918040750/https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s00299-004-0767-1|dead-url=no}}</ref>第一种转基因家畜于1985年<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.nature.com/articles/nbt783|pages=157–162|title=Cloned transgenic cattle produce milk with higher levels of β-casein and κ-casein|journal=Nature Biotechnology|volume=21|issue=2|issn=1546-1696|date=2003/02|language=En|accessdate=2018-04-02|doi=10.1038/nbt783|author=Brigid Brophy, Grant Smolenski, Thomas Wheeler, David Wells, Phil L'Huillier, Götz Laible|archive-date=2022-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220604144742/https://www.nature.com/articles/nbt783}}</ref>通过微注射外源DNA入兔，羊，猪的卵产生<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.nature.com/doifinder/10.1038/315680a0|pages=680–683|title=Production of transgenic rabbits, sheep and pigs by microinjection|journal=Nature|volume=315|issue=6021|issn=1476-4687|date=1985/06|language=En|accessdate=2018-04-02|doi=10.1038/315680a0|author=Robert E. Hammer, Vernon G. Pursel, Caird E. Rexroad, Robert J. Wall, Douglas J. Bolt, Karl M. Ebert, Richard D. Palmiter, Ralph L. Brinster}}</ref>。第一种被用来在它们的乳汁中合成蛋白质的转基因动物是老鼠，<ref name = Clark>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Mammary Gland Biology and Neoplasia|volume=3|number=3|pages=337–350|title=The Mammary Gland as a Bioreactor: Expression, Processing, and Production of Recombinant Proteins|author=A. John Clark}}</ref>以生产人类组织型[[纤溶酶|纤溶酶原]]激活剂<ref>{{cite journal|author=K. Gordon, E. Lee, J. Vitale, A. Smith, H. Westphal, and L. Hennighausen|year=1987|title=Production of human tissue plasmnogen activator in transgenic mouse milk|journal=Biotechnology|volume=5|page=1183±1187}}</ref>该技术现在已经应用到羊，猪，牛和其他家畜。<ref name = Clark/>

随着[[microRNA|microRNA]]在1993年被发现<ref>{{cite journal|last=Lee|first=R.C.|coauthors=Ambros, V.|title=The C. elegans heterochronic gene lin-4 encodes small RNAs with antisense complementarity to lin-14.|journal=Cell|year=1993}}</ref>利用[[RNA干扰|RNA干扰]]来沉默生物内源性基因变得可能。[[克雷格·梅洛|克雷格·梅洛]]和[[安德鲁·法厄|安德鲁·法厄]]在1998年发现了通过注射双链RNA进入[[秀丽隐杆线虫|秀丽隐杆线虫]]''(C. elegans)''可以达到沉默的效果。<ref name="Fire">{{cite journal |author=Fire A, Xu S, Montgomery M, Kostas S, Driver S, Mello C |title=Potent and specific genetic interference by double-stranded RNA in ''Caenorhabditis elegans'' |journal=Nature |volume=391 |issue=6669 |pages=806–11 |year=1998 |pmid=9486653 |doi=10.1038/35888 |bibcode=1998Natur.391..806F}}</ref>利用基因工程，microRNA可以长期地，永久地沉默靶基因。在2002年，稳定的基因沉默在单个哺乳动物细胞中被诱导<ref>{{cite journal|title=A System for Stable Expression of Short Interfering RNAs in Mammalian Cells|journal=Science|date=2002-04-19|doi=10.1126/science.1068999|url=http://science.sciencemag.org/content/296/5567/550|language=en|volume=296|issue=5567|pages=550–553|issn=0036-8075|accessdate=2018-04-02|author=Thijn R. Brummelkamp, René Bernards, Reuven Agami|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125203145/https://science.sciencemag.org/content/296/5567/550|dead-url=no}}</ref>在2005年，完成了在整个小鼠层次完成沉默<ref>{{cite journal|pages=2252–2256|title=A transgenic approach for RNA interference-based genetic screening in mice|volume=103|issue=7|date=2006-02-14|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences|url=http://www.pnas.org/cgi/doi/10.1073/pnas.0511034103|accessdate=2018-04-02|author=Shaohua Peng, J. Philippe York, Pumin Zhang|doi=10.1073/pnas.0511034103}}</ref>在2007年发表的论文中，昆虫和线虫的基因形成的microRNA被放进植物，导致摄入的转基因植物的害虫基因沉默。<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.nature.com/articles/cr2011164|pages=3–5|title=Ingested plant miRNAs regulate gene expression in animals|journal=Cell Research|volume=22|issue=1|issn=1748-7838|date=2012/01|language=En|accessdate=2018-04-02|doi=10.1038/cr.2011.164|author=Hervé Vaucheret, Yves Chupeau|archive-date=2022-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220415172708/https://www.nature.com/articles/cr2011164}}</ref>

==商业化==
1976年[[基因泰克|基因泰克]]，第一个基因工程公司由[[赫伯特·博耶|赫伯特·博耶]]和[[罗伯特·斯旺森|罗伯特·斯旺森]]成立，一年后该公司开始在大肠杆菌中生产人类蛋白质（[[生长抑素|生长抑素]]） 。基因泰克公司在1978年宣布生产人[[胰岛素|胰岛素]]。<ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.1073/pnas.76.1.106|last=Goeddel|first=David|coauthors=Dennis G. Kleid, Francisco Bolivar, Herbert L. Heyneker, Daniel G. Yansura, Roberto Crea, Tadaaki Hirose, Adam Kraszewski, Keiichi Itakura, AND Arthur D. Riggs|title=Expression in Escherichia coli of chemically synthesized genes for human insulin|journal=PNAS|date=January 1979|volume=76|issue=1|pages=106–110|url=http://www.pnas.org/content/76/1/106.full.pdf|pmid=85300|pmc=382885|bibcode=1979PNAS...76..106G|access-date=2014-01-27|archive-date=2017-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171115230742/http://www.pnas.org/content/76/1/106.full.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>在1980年，[[美国最高法院|美国最高法院]]在[[戴蒙德诉查克拉巴蒂案|戴蒙德诉查克拉巴蒂案]]一案中裁定，基因改造的生物可以申请专利。<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://supreme.justia.com/us/447/303/case.html|title=Diamond V Chakrabarty|volume=447|author=US Supreme Court Cases from Justia & Oyez|publisher=Supreme.justia.com|date=16 June 1980|accessdate=17 July 2010|archive-date=2012-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120107012535/http://supreme.justia.com/us/447/303/case.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>由细菌产生的胰岛素，商标名[[药用胰岛素|药用胰岛素]]，于1982年被[[美国食品和药物管理局|美国食品和药物管理局]]批准。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,949646-1,00.html |title=Artificial Genes |publisher=TIME |date=15 November 1982 |accessdate=17 July 2010 |archive-date=2013-05-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130521070027/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,949646-1,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>在1983年，一家生物技术公司，“高级遗传科学”（AGS）申请在美国政府授权下进行“[[:en:Ice-minus_bacteria|冰<sup>-</sup>]]”丁香假單胞菌细菌的田间试验，以保护农作物免于霜冻，但环保团体和示威者的法律挑战推迟了田间试验四年之久。<ref>Rebecca Bratspies (2007) Some Thoughts on the American Approach to Regulating Genetically Modified Organisms.  Kansas Journal of Law and Public Policy 16:393 [http://nationalaglawcenter.org/assets/bibarticles/bratspies_some.pdf]{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>1987年，“[[:en:Ice-minus_bacteria|冰<sup>-</sup>]]”丁香假單胞菌成为第一个被释放到环境中的[[转基因生物|转基因生物]]，<ref name=BBC2002>BBC News 14 June 2002 [http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/science/nature/2045286.stm GM crops: A bitter harvest?] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/science/nature/2045286.stm |date=20220419232302 }}</ref>被喷在了加州草莓场和马铃薯田地上。<ref>Thomas H. Maugh II for the Los Angeles Times. June 09, 1987.  [http://articles.latimes.com/1987-06-09/news/mn-6024_1_frost-damage Altered Bacterium Does Its Job : Frost Failed to Damage Sprayed Test Crop, Company Says] {{Wayback|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1987-06-09/news/mn-6024_1_frost-damage |date=20160305212700 }}</ref>兩片試驗田俱在實驗前夕遭到示威者破壞。[[BBC|BBC]]描述此事為「史上第一片試驗田遇到史上第一批破壞者」。<ref name=BBC2002 />

[[转基因植物|转基因植物]]的首次田间试验在法国和美国于1986年进行，试验对象是耐[[除草剂|除草剂]]烟草。<ref>{{cite web|last=James|first=Clive|title=Global Review of the Field Testing and Commercialization of Transgenic Plants: 1986 to 1995|url=http://www.isaaa.org/kc/Publications/pdfs/isaaabriefs/Briefs%201.pdf|publisher=The International Service for the Acquisition of Agri-biotech Applications|accessdate=17 July 2010|year=1996|archive-date=2019-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190724004503/http://www.isaaa.org/kc/Publications/pdfs/isaaabriefs/Briefs%201.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>中华人民共和国是首个商业化的转基因植物的国家，于1992年引入抗病毒烟草。<ref name="James1997">{{cite journal|author=James, Clive|year=1997|title=Global Status of Transgenic Crops in 1997|journal=ISAAA Briefs No. 5.|pages=31|url=http://www.isaaa.org/resources/publications/briefs/05/download/isaaa-brief-05-1997.pdf|access-date=2014-01-27|archive-date=2018-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181222181829/http://www.isaaa.org/resources/publications/briefs/05/download/isaaa-brief-05-1997.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>1994年[[孟山都#分拆及合併|Calgene公司]]获得批准商业化[[:en:Flavr_SAVR|:en:Flavr SAVR]]番茄，一种被设计有较长保质期的番茄。 <ref>{{cite journal|url=http://californiaagriculture.ucanr.edu/landingpage.cfm?articleid=ca.v054n04p6|pages=6–7|title=The case of the FLAVR SAVR tomato|journal=California Agriculture|volume=54|issue=4|date=2000-07-01|issn=0008-0845|language=en|accessdate=2018-04-02|doi=10.3733/ca.v054n04p6|author=G. Bruening, J.M. Lyons|archive-date=2016-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160412181545/http://californiaagriculture.ucanr.edu/landingpage.cfm?articleid=ca.v054n04p6|dead-url=no}}</ref>1994年，欧盟批准了耐除草剂[[溴苯腈|溴苯腈]]的烟草，使得它成为第一个在欧洲商业化的基因工程作物。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Transgenic tobacco is European first|date=18 June 1994|author=Debora MacKenzie|url=http://www.newscientist.com/article/mg14219301.100-transgenic-tobacco-is-european-first.html|publisher=New Scientist|access-date=2014-01-27|archive-date=2015-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150521011003/http://www.newscientist.com/article/mg14219301.100-transgenic-tobacco-is-european-first.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>1995年，转Bt基因马铃薯在被美国FDA批准之后，被美国安全环境保护局批准，成为在美国首个自产农药的作物。<ref>[http://news.google.co.uk/newspapers?id=A0YyAAAAIBAJ&sjid=jOYFAAAAIBAJ&pg=4631,1776980&dq=bacillus+thuringiensis+potato+1996+approved&hl= Genetically Altered Potato Ok'd For Crops] {{Wayback|url=http://news.google.co.uk/newspapers?id=A0YyAAAAIBAJ&sjid=jOYFAAAAIBAJ&pg=4631,1776980&dq=bacillus+thuringiensis+potato+1996+approved&hl= |date=20181105224857 }} Lawrence Journal-World - 6 May 1995</ref>到2010年，按照[[ISAAA|ISAAA]]年度简报： “虽然只有29个国家（或地区，下同）在2010年商业化种植转基因作物，但加上另外的31个国家，自从1996年以来，共计60个国家已授予监管机构批准转基因作物作为进口食品和饲料使用和释放到环境的权力....共有1,045批文，授权针对25种植物的196个案例。（注：一个“案例”是对一个特定物种的特定基因改造）。因此，在60个国家中，转基因作物已被接受进口作为食品和饲料使用和释放到环境中：包括主要的粮食进口国，如（不种植转基因作物的）日本。已批准转基因作物的60个国家中，美国的批文位列榜首，其次是日本，加拿大，墨西哥，韩国，澳大利亚，菲律宾，新西兰，欧盟，台湾。玉米获得的批准最多（65），其次是棉（39），油菜（15），马铃薯和大豆（各14）。在大多数国家，获批最多的案例是耐除草剂大豆（GTS-40-3-2），共25项批文（欧盟的27项计为1项），其次是抗虫玉米MON810（23项批文），耐除草剂玉米NK603（22）和抗虫棉MON1445（14）。”<ref>[http://www.isaaa.org/resources/publications/briefs/43/executivesummary/default.asp Global Status of Commercialized Biotech/GM Crops: 2011] {{Wayback|url=http://www.isaaa.org/resources/publications/briefs/43/executivesummary/default.asp |date=20200613053857 }} ISAAA Brief ISAAA Brief 43-2011. Retrieved 14 October 2012</ref>

==反对==
对基因工程的利用，支持和反对的声音从技术被开发之初就存在了。在Árpád Pusztai[[:en:Pusztai_affair|发表了他1998年的研究]]后，公众对基因改造食物的反对有所增加<ref>[http://www.guardian.co.uk/education/2008/jan/15/academicexperts.highereducationprofile Arpad Pusztai: Biological divide] {{Wayback|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/education/2008/jan/15/academicexperts.highereducationprofile |date=20130318005752 }} James Randerson [[卫报|卫报]] 2008.1.15</ref>

